                            <h3>Admissions</h3>

                                <p>PMBA welcomes applications from well-rounded individuals with minimum 3 years’ work experience who bring unique insight to the classroom learning environment and team experience.</p>

<p>Follow these steps to apply:</p>

<ol>
    <li>Complete the <a href="http://www.graduate.ucf.edu">online application</a> and remit the $30 application fee.</li>
    <li>Submit all required documents, including official undergraduate transcripts, GMAT or GRE test scores, three letters of recommendation, and a career goal statement outlining your 5- and 10-year objectives, and explaining how the PMBA program will assist you in obtaining these goals.</li>
<li>Schedule an interview with the PMBA Admissions Committee.</li>

</ol>
