                            <h3>Tuition Schedule</h3>

                                <p>The tuition for the PMBA program is an all-inclusive package. It covers all tuition costs, textbooks, laptop computer, orientation and graduation events, parking during class times, class shirt, lifetime membership to the UCF Alumni Association, and all administrative fees. The tuition is the same for Florida residents and non-residents.</p> 

<p>Many employers offer PMBA reimbursement packages. Please check with your employer to determine the availability of financial assistance.</p>

<p>Participants of the PMBA program are often eligible for financial aid. Contact <a href="http://finaid.ucf.edu">UCF’s Financial Aid department</a> for more information.</p>

